<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_atf_test"><sys_atf_test action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><copied_from/><description>Desc: IMACD :  Remove Request level approval stage from workflow renderer
Testing Steps:
Submit catalog item specific to MPS
In the filter nav - go to sc_req_item.list
If not present, add stage to the columns list
Click gear\cog in the left corner
